== Setup a first rails project with Git

rails new .
git init .
echo ".*.swp" >> .gitignore
git add .gitignore
git commit -m 'Added .gitignore'
git add app/ config/ config.ru db/ doc/ Gemfile lib/ log/ public/ Rakefile README script/ test/ tmp/ vendor/
git commit -m 'Initial files'
bundle install
# This is for phusion-passenger deployment:
# bundle install --path vendor/cache
rake db:migrate

== Create the sandbow application

rails generate model user
rake db:migrate 
rake db:test:load
ruby -Itest test/unit/user_test.rb
